without any human oversight.

11:11.875 --> 11:13.625
Me neither.

11:14.458 --> 11:17.291
But it might take a while
to find another job.

11:17.375 --> 11:20.583
You said it yourself.
The data migration boom is over.

11:21.875 --> 11:23.041
It's the cloud.

11:24.458 --> 11:25.541
The cloud.

11:26.958 --> 11:30.250
So I need you to get on board, okay?

11:31.166 --> 11:34.166
Come on. It's our last Christmas here.

11:34.250 --> 11:36.250
Let's try to enjoy it.

11:39.125 --> 11:41.500
Tons of fun.

12:03.666 --> 12:04.666
Hunter?

12:04.750 --> 12:08.916
Hey, Pama-lama-ding-dong!
Guess what? We're outside!

12:11.375 --> 12:13.000
