- Queen Latifah.

12:13.083 --> 12:15.041
Get up. Your brother's here.

12:16.625 --> 12:17.625
God.

12:29.583 --> 12:31.416
Damn it.

12:33.541 --> 12:34.958
Gosh, I miss the snow!

12:35.916 --> 12:38.791
- Hey. What are you doing...
- Doing here?

12:38.875 --> 12:41.750
We flew in early to get ahead of
snowpocalypse or whatever.

12:41.833 --> 12:43.416
Snowmageddon.

12:43.500 --> 12:45.333
Snowpocalypse is better.

12:45.416 --> 12:47.583
Hey, babe. Hurry up.

12:48.750 --> 12:50.250
- Coming, baby!
- Who's that? Aah.

12:50.333 --> 12:52.333
Pamuel L. Jackson! Bring it in.

12:52.416 --> 12:53.916
Hi, Hunter. Hi.

12:54.666 --> 12:56.583
Here she is!

12:57.291 --> 12:59.166
Oh. Careful.

13:10.125 --> 13:11.291
- Okay! Hey.
- Oh!

13:11.375 --> 13:14.375
Oh, we would've called, but we thought
it would be fun to surprise you.

13:14.458 --> 13:15.541
- Yeah.
- Are you surprised?

13:15.625 --> 13:18.041
We are surprised. We're very surprised.

13:18.125 --> 13:19.583
I know. It's so cute here.

13:19.666 --> 13:21.666
- Aunt Mei!
- So quaint... Hi!

13:21.750 --> 13:22.750
Hi, my adorables.

13:22.833 --> 13:24.517
I didn't think you were coming
till tomorrow.

13:24.541 --> 13:25.541
I'm here now.

13:25.625 --> 13:29.250
We all thought she was coming tomorrow,
but she's come in the dead of night.

13:29.958 --> 13:31.750
Hey, Ollie, look who it is.

13:31.833 --> 13:35.250
- It's Uncle Jeff. Hey.
- Hey, buddy!

13:35.333 --> 13:37.041
Ollie, look! Snow!

13:37.958 --> 13:39.166
Good to see you, buddy.

13:39.250 --> 13:40.791
He has gotten so big.

13:40.875 --> 13:42.166
Okay!

13:42.250 --> 13:44.458
Oh, my gosh, I'm so sorry.

13:44.541 --> 13:47.375
It's the last one.
It's the last one. I promise, okay?

13:48.041 --> 13:49.250
That's enough.

13:49.333 --> 13:52.083
Mind giving our luggage a tuggage?
I wanna get that guy situated.

13:57.333 --> 13:58.458
Wow.

13:59.333 --> 14:00.875
Yeah, we had a great year.

14:02.083 --> 14:04.041
Oh, great arm, buddy!

14:04.125 --> 14:06.666
- Ollie, that is not a toy.
- I'll get it.

14:09.416 --> 14:10.958
We're teaching him Spanish!

14:11.041 --> 14:13.416
What did I tell you about taking
other people's stuff?

14:13.500 --> 14:16.833
- Where do you have us set up?
- Oh, in the den on the pullout.

14:16.916 --> 14:20.708
Okay.
In the den on the pullout. Yeah, okay.

14:42.333 --> 14:44.833
Wow, that lady wasn't kidding.

14:48.166 --> 14:49.166
What?

15:02.166 --> 15:04.958
What... Where is it?

15:10.416 --> 15:14.583
That brat kid stole my doll.
My mom's doll.

15:18.208 --> 15:19.583
How am I gonna find this kid?

15:20.500 --> 15:22.208
Maxwell Johan Mercer.

15:22.291 --> 15:23.750
Carol Ellen Mercer.

15:24.875 --> 15:26.125
Bingo.

15:39.000 --> 15:41.375
You have arrived at your destination.

15:41.458 --> 15:43.625
Get in the car!

15:44.250 --> 15:47.791
You need to get in a car now.
We are so late. You have no idea.

15:47.875 --> 15:50.000
- Gotcha!
- What was that for?

15:50.083 --> 15:51.559
- I legit might cry right now.
- Don't!

15:51.583 --> 15:53.291
I need that for cheerleading, you cretin.

15:53.375 --> 15:54.875
Son of a sandwich!

15:54.958 --> 15:58.208
Get in the car!

15:58.291 --> 16:00.583
We're gonna miss the flight,
you guys. Come on!

16:00.666 --> 16:02.958
Uh, hi, my dude. Um...

16:03.041 --> 16:04.625
Is Carol Mercer home?

16:04.708 --> 16:06.767
No, Carol took the early flight.
She booked the cars.

16:06.791 --> 16:09.226
That's why they're in her name.
These are our cars. We need to go.

16:09.250 --> 16:10.833
Will you be a mensch?

16:10.916 --> 16:12.625
- Put that in the back for us, huh?
- Uhâ€¦

16:12.708 --> 16:15.458
Bethany, is this a good time
