Text that to me.
Okay, guys, get in the car!

16:21.291 --> 16:22.666
Give your stuff to the driver.

16:22.750 --> 16:25.083
- If I miss the duty-free shopâ€¦
- I'm not the driver.

16:25.166 --> 16:27.291
â€¦I am going to shave somebody's head.
