17:27.375 --> 17:28.375
Armed.

17:31.708 --> 17:33.250
Here we go. All right.

17:36.458 --> 17:38.458
I'm sorry,
but I really do need to talk to Carol.

17:38.541 --> 17:42.541
Yes. Don't worry. I'll make sure that
Carol gives you five stars in the app.

17:42.625 --> 17:43.958
Reputation is everything.

17:45.458 --> 17:48.541
Oh, hey, wait! Wait!

17:55.708 --> 17:57.583
What the heck are you looking at?

18:04.333 --> 18:06.791
I'm sorry. I'm having a bad day.

18:15.583 --> 18:16.625
There it is.

18:19.250 --> 18:21.125
Oh, myâ€¦

