19:01.458 --> 19:03.958
I'm a good, normal man.
I'm gonna talk to Pam.

19:04.666 --> 19:05.666
Pam.

19:05.750 --> 19:07.375
I'm just a neighbor helping.

19:07.458 --> 19:09.625
I water their dogs... plants.

19:09.708 --> 19:13.291
I'm a friend of Carol's. A friend of...
